com.iha.emulator.models.value

Class AbstractValue<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.iha.emulator.models.value.AbstractValue<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - data type set by class extending this abstract class, used in compilation
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    HasGenerator, Value<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BoilerModeActuatorValue, BoilerStatusSensorValue, BoilerTypeActuatorValue, EmissionsSensorValue, EmptyValue, HumiditySensorValue, LightSensorValue, NoiseSensorValue, OnOffActuatorValue, OnOffSensorValue, OpenClosedSensorValue, PressureSensorValue, TemperatureActuatorValue, TemperatureSensorValue

    public abstract class AbstractValue<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Value<T>, HasGenerator
    Abstract class providing implementation of Value interface methods used by all specific value implementations.
    Author:
    Filip Sutovsky
